# Database Connection (Pooler for queries - Port 6543)
# IMPORTANT: Add ?pgbouncer=true&connection_limit=1 for connection pooling (Railway, Supabase pooler)
# Example: postgresql://user:pass@host:6543/db?pgbouncer=true&connection_limit=1
